text: Zavodsky City District is the name of several city divisions in Russia. *Zavodsky City District, Kemerovo, a city district of Kemerovo, the administrative center of Kemerovo Oblast *Zavodsky City District, Novokuznetsk, a city district of Novokuznetsk, a city in Kemerovo Oblast ==See also== *Zavodskoy (disambiguation) *Zavodsky (disambiguation) ==References==
